<plot>This video documentary gives film fans a behind-the-scenes look at this classic story of suspense and revenge. With scenes from both the 1962 original and the 1991 remake of this story about a lawyer trying to protect his family from a man he helped send to prison, this documentary looks at the work of the cast and crew that went into making the film such a success.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?573817</url></doc>
